    <description>Various helpers to simplify cross-platform development with Xamarin.Forms.

Available utilities:

- Get device screen size
- Get current culture info
- Get image size by path
- The very basic image resize
- Box view with rounded corners + shadow support on iOS

Details and samples are available on the project's website:
https://github.com/TheUniforms/Uniforms-Core</description>
